Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.08,0:26:41.44,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}因为我只有您
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.68,0:26:54.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}虚伪的童话 在我心中来回碰撞 当当作响
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.28,0:27:00.60,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}即便是没有客人的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.60,0:27:14.12,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}您亦带着一副悲伤的神情 坚持起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:18.76,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我爱着您的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:23.48,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}请让我把您夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:31.20,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}这个得不到救赎的故事中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.52,0:27:36.04,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}一瞬间便好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.04,0:27:40.32,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}请您只注视我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:49.36,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}这便是我的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:55.24,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}不管触摸多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:28:06.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}这份感情 依然无法传达给您
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.84,0:28:12.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}但人是会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.28,0:28:15.92,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}因此您不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:26.96,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}不管命运受到了什么咀咒 我也要传达给您
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:35.96,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我爱着您的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.96,0:28:40.68,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}包括您的伤痕 您的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.88,0:28:48.36,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}您的罪恶 您的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.60,0:28:58.00,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}我的一切都被您夺去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:05.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}现在 我依然是您的人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.60,0:29:12.28,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&H4928B7&}所以 请留在我的身边
